Cell["\<\
Predict works for prediction in an analogous way as Classify for \
classification.

The prediction of the trained predictor is a numerical value (not a class):\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7774408507789497`*^9, 3.777440877098627*^9}, {
  3.814088663905182*^9, 
