Cell["\<\
If the uncertainty of the prediction is taken into account, it looks \
reasonable when compared with the training data.

Here, I consider one standard deviation (68% of chances that the prediction \
will fall within this range)\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7774452150978394`*^9, 3.777445275288288*^9}, {
  3.777445711368511*^9, 3.77744573840858*^9}, {3.7801370953889847`*^9, 
