   3.781321027896296*^9, 
   3.7813210304594407`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a0cd458b-763e-4f8c-99d0-\
e1a68bb44956"],

Cell["Nearest neighbours: Similar idea to KNN method in ", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.781275739424556*^9, 3.7812757979973297`*^9}, {
  3.781276028684903*^9, 3.781276029415653*^9}, {3.7812761939095497`*^9, 
  3.7812762091536493`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"0e4e0033-ee25-45bc-9a88-\
7f4a6c44b5d7"],

Cell["Decision tree: Used both for classification and prediction. ", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.781275739424556*^9, 3.7812757979973297`*^9}, {
   3.781276028684903*^9, 3.781276052138295*^9}, {3.78127609748188*^9, 
   3.7812761030392766`*^9}, {3.7812761352789564`*^9, 3.7812761651678543`*^9}, 
   3.814100225268145*^9},ExpressionUUID->"d52d7920-7805-4dd2-a67b-\
eab45cc57d19"],

Cell["Neural network: Later...", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.781275739424556*^9, 3.7812757979973297`*^9}, {
  3.781276028684903*^9, 3.781276050903968*^9}, {3.781276091085929*^9, 
  3.781276106259449*^9}, {3.7812761682351866`*^9, 
  3.7812761897232895`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"cba65cb1-a113-4bb9-aa22-\
8265c4938555"],

Cell["\<\
Other implemented in Mathematica: \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]GradientBoostedTrees\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote], \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]RandomForest\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] , \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]GaussianProcess\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.781275739424556*^9, 3.7812757979973297`*^9}, {
  3.781276028684903*^9, 3.781276050903968*^9}, {3.781276091085929*^9, 
  3.7812761049279127`*^9}, {3.781276216702717*^9, 
  3.781276252981552*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"17cccf1a-7905-42ac-aa84-\
4e6430813c37"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[TextData[{
 "One can specify a method in the ",
 StyleBox["Predict", "CodeText"],
 " function as follows: \n\n",
 StyleBox["Predict[", "CodeText"],
 StyleBox["training data", "CodeText",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 StyleBox[", Method", "CodeText"],
 StyleBox[Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
    "\[Rule]", " ", 
     "\"\<\!\(\*StyleBox[\"method\",FontSlant->\"Italic\"]\)\!\(\*StyleBox[\" \
\",FontSlant->\"Italic\"]\)\!\(\*StyleBox[\"name\",FontSlant->\"Italic\"]\)\>\
\""}], "]"}], TraditionalForm]], "CodeText",ExpressionUUID->
  "41aab29e-8696-4179-8781-5d5d4f48a279"], "CodeText"],
 "\n\nAs for classification, if no method is specified, Mathematica will try \
several and present results for the method with lowest cost function."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.781276501655258*^9, 3.781276564651207*^9}, {
  3.7812767167849207`*^9, 3.7812767305978127`*^9}, {3.781320961953904*^9, 
  3.781321015910694*^9}, {3.7813211585742793`*^9, 
  3.781321160299463*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"d8a0169e-3063-45a9-a117-\
1bf24d6f6a74"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Linear regression", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.78127368033797*^9, 
  3.781273683026927*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"995be3b7-22e1-4e6e-aa2f-\
f16b051b819e"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["General formulation", "Subsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.781424871937063*^9, 
  3.7814248745863667`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"faece4d7-c272-4c69-9dfe-\
d386f4711205"],

Cell[TextData[{
 StyleBox["Features:",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 " Suppose that we have a data set in which instances are characterised by ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["M", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "9c4d6d0f-22ff-44e4-a33c-62d182f922fd"],
 " numerical features: ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    StyleBox["x",
     FontWeight->"Bold"], " ", "=", " "}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "d9836fc4-0ada-4527-94a9-ee8228202342"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{
     SubscriptBox["x", "1"], ",", 
     SubscriptBox["x", "2"], ",", "...", ",", 
     SubscriptBox["x", "M"]}], "}"}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "9df41fb1-36fc-4617-b371-ed4f68c745bf"],
 "\n\n",
 StyleBox["Dependent variable:",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 " For each example in the data set, we are also given a ",
 StyleBox["variable ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["y", TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"c3d14496-366d-4f40-b05d-7ebe4801085a"],
 " that depends on the features, ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   StyleBox["x",
    FontWeight->"Bold"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "e5490bd3-3de3-47ee-869a-02644bee352e"],
 ".\n\n",
 StyleBox["Aim:",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 " Given an unseen example with feature vector ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    StyleBox["x",
     FontWeight->"Bold"], "'"}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "68adda3c-830b-43f6-a6f9-bd7b54602de1"],
 ", we want to predict the value corresponding to the dependent variable, ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["y", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "4423ad9d-e814-4014-bf84-72e7999ee224"],
 "."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7814238413322234`*^9, 3.7814239580418854`*^9}, {
  3.7814241506723614`*^9, 3.7814242431552496`*^9}, {3.781424292943878*^9, 
  3.781424386036137*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"210bdc67-7f0a-4a7c-b5c7-\
5ff4ae4f9042"],

Cell["Two assumption:", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7814242507682524`*^9, 
  3.78142426224026*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"c93a6de8-17d5-42d6-a862-\
74783015b39f"],

Cell["\<\
The dependent variable can be expressed as a linear combination of the \
features:\
\>", "ItemNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.781424286492959*^9, 3.7814242909182024`*^9}, {
  3.781424380353567*^9, 
  3.7814244161537485`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"31eea900-0d3c-47b5-a5eb-\
c959f3ff99b0"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "\t",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"y", "=", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"f", "(", 
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{"x", ";", " ", 
            SubscriptBox["w", "0"]}], ",", 
           StyleBox["w",
            FontWeight->"Bold"]}], ")"}], "\[Congruent]", 
         RowBox[{
          SubscriptBox["w", "0"], "+", 
          RowBox[{
           SubscriptBox["w", "1"], 
           SubscriptBox["x", "1"]}], "+", 
          RowBox[{
           SubscriptBox["w", "2"], 
           SubscriptBox["x", "2"]}], "+"}]}], "..."}], ".", 
       RowBox[{"+", 
        SubscriptBox["w", "M"]}]}], 
      SubscriptBox["x", "M"]}], "+", "\[Epsilon]"}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"43f0faad-8f5f-4c3c-9bd9-bf9ec37e07bf"]
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7814244387087636`*^9, 3.78142452201871*^9}, 
   3.781424552238443*^9, {3.78142819774783*^9, 3.7814282074332385`*^9}, {
   3.781428239627142*^9, 3.781428239627142*^9}, {3.7814299914028745`*^9, 
   3.7814299914028745`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"afd252a5-48a8-4bce-9dda-\
537430108355"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "\tThis can also be written with more compact notations as\t\n\t ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"f", "(", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"x", ";", " ", 
       SubscriptBox["w", "0"]}], ",", 
      StyleBox["w",
       FontWeight->"Bold"]}], ")"}], "=", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{
      SubscriptBox["w", "0"], "+", 
      RowBox[{
       UnderoverscriptBox["\[Sum]", 
        RowBox[{"i", "=", "1"}], "M"], 
       RowBox[{
        SubscriptBox["w", "i"], 
        SubscriptBox["x", "i"]}]}], "+", "\[Epsilon]"}], "=", 
     RowBox[{
      SubscriptBox["w", "0"], "+", 
      RowBox[{
       SuperscriptBox[
        StyleBox["w",
         FontWeight->"Bold"], "T"], 
       StyleBox["x",
        FontWeight->"Bold"]}], " ", "+", "\[Epsilon]"}]}]}], 
   TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->"34872d0c-ec4f-4242-ae4f-bb214d81a912"],
 ", \t      ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    SuperscriptBox[
     StyleBox["w",
      FontWeight->"Bold"], "T"], "=", 
    RowBox[{"(", 
     RowBox[{
      SubscriptBox["w", "1"], ",", 
      SubscriptBox["w", "2"], ",", "...", ",", 
      SubscriptBox["w", "M"]}], ")"}]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "84db391f-a5de-4d27-835c-cfd846538aea"],
 ",  ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    StyleBox["x",
     FontWeight->"Bold"], "="}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "32cf5e13-ce99-4f39-8a46-992170bf08a3"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"(", GridBox[{
      {
       SubscriptBox["x", "1"]},
      {
       SubscriptBox["x", "2"]},
      {"..."},
      {
       SubscriptBox["x", "M"]}
     }], ")"}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "0217fa43-59d5-49be-b3e9-965e74bd4b83"]
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7814244387087636`*^9, 3.78142452201871*^9}, 
   3.781424552238443*^9, {3.781426304386639*^9, 3.7814263646355147`*^9}, {
   3.7814282476059484`*^9, 3.781428248794654*^9}, {3.781428327739781*^9, 
   3.7814285620006213`*^9}, {3.7814289116912856`*^9, 3.781428916877062*^9}, {
   3.7814299879746428`*^9, 
   3.7814299879746428`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"cc831616-bb7d-4725-bbec-\
d01897bdf813"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Here, ", "ItemParagraph",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.781424564962476*^9, 
  3.7814245658687143`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"7e42e908-d4cc-4e49-89d9-\
6675fa0abd45"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[TextData[{
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["w", "0"], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->"TraditionalForm",ExpressionUUID->
  "262f57b6-450e-429c-a131-a18a3bd6f2cd"],
 " is the intercept"
}], "Subitem",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.781424598864729*^9, 
  3.781424618498206*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"94cee8b5-b363-4a74-a685-\
ecb5704aef6b"],

Cell[TextData[{
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{
     SubscriptBox["w", "1"], ",", 
     SubscriptBox["w", "2"], ",", "...", ",", 
     SubscriptBox["w", "M"]}], "}"}], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->"TraditionalForm",ExpressionUUID->
  "529ad949-2be4-41f3-80cc-b5ac84a43f80"],
 " are the weight of each feature to explain the dependent variable ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["y", TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->"TraditionalForm",ExpressionUUID->
  "6de0702e-17e0-42cf-870d-0831f06206f7"]
}], "Subitem",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.781424598864729*^9, 
  3.781424698952506*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"cbf5aacf-966c-438c-97c4-\
9487e358bb1e"],

Cell[TextData[{
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["\[Epsilon]", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "14379cf9-7d4d-4af5-a60f-1b9c15271c5a"],
 " is the residual error between the linear prediction and the true response"
}], "Subitem",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.781424598864729*^9, 3.7814247911236205`*^9}, {
  3.7814250706098137`*^9, 
  3.7814250935153637`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"cfd95290-7dbb-422a-bdca-\
d56a4de4dd47"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
The residual error is often assumed to obey a normal distribution:\
\>", "ItemNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.781425112395906*^9, 3.781425136156145*^9}, {
  3.8141018439629354`*^9, 
  3.814101850004284*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"3351aff1-05ac-4dc6-879c-\
c36e097ebe99"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[TextData[Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{"\t", 
   RowBox[{"\[Epsilon]", "~", 
    RowBox[{"N", "(", 
     RowBox[{"\[Mu]", ",", 
      SuperscriptBox["\[Sigma]", "2"]}], ")"}]}]}], 
  TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->"d539f4f5-54c3-4354-b9a7-9de0f0ce6213"]], \
"Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7814251414035196`*^9, 
  3.781425174256424*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"36b72aed-b113-41c7-9c8a-\
6b58b6e5ac7d"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Fitting the model to data", "Subsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.781425398080696*^9, 
  3.781425402272953*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"ccd3f6fd-c0af-4f5d-b830-\
c4a0ed2b1536"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "To train a linear model from data, we need to find the values of the \
parameters ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{
     SubscriptBox["w", "0"], ",", 
     SubscriptBox["w", "1"], ",", 
     SubscriptBox["w", "2"], ",", "...", ",", 
     SubscriptBox["w", "M"]}], "}"}], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->"TraditionalForm",ExpressionUUID->
  "46c48a5a-82d4-4b63-9b7d-b3983274046a"],
 " and the distribution for \[Epsilon] that gives the better fit of the model \
to the data."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7814254079251533`*^9, 3.7814254290348783`*^9}, {
  3.781425661125416*^9, 3.7814256842736015`*^9}, {3.7814258180258512`*^9, 
  3.7814259029823112`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"7c0ec9c8-af57-43ff-9121-\
836bc730f04b"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "For 1-dimensional data (one feature, ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"M", " ", "=", " ", "1"}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "1b83ef49-7296-4ed6-a3ed-2b7625a35d48"],
 "), we just need to find the straight line that is closest to all the points \
in the training dataset.\n\nIn other words, the line ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"f", "(", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"x", ";", " ", 
      SubscriptBox["w", "0"]}], ",", 
     StyleBox["w",
      FontWeight->"Bold"]}], ")"}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "800a382e-c804-4cec-ad4d-0d080aa27ad0"],
 " for which the distance of the data to the line is minimized."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.781425905796846*^9, 3.781425927504614*^9}, {
  3.781426006787908*^9, 3.78142603227083*^9}, {3.7814286026006083`*^9, 
  3.7814286336301026`*^9}, {3.7814299597019525`*^9, 
  3.781429971518936*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"e2c06d92-18c6-4ecf-baec-\
06f877b10774"],

