Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Using linear model fit function", "Subsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7814443527515855`*^9, 
  3.7814443639274235`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"7d49181c-cee1-4ec8-8f41-\
0596cc6ccd9c"],

Cell["\<\
As shown above, Wolfram Language can be used to train a predictor based on \
the linear regression model.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.781444426252282*^9, 
  3.781444482101815*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"7193295b-2435-48ef-8812-\
c170c63fa999"],

Cell["\<\
A linear model can also be fitted using the LinearModelFit function with the \
following syntax:\
\>", "Text",
