Cell["\<\
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]Guess who\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] is played by two \
players. Each player gets a random picture from a character. The goal is to \
guess the name of the character chosen by your opponent. This is done by \
asking questions in turn to infer the features of your opponent\
\[CloseCurlyQuote]s character. Typical questions are:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7803217939860506`*^9, 3.7803218751302776`*^9}, {
