Cell["Testing the performance of the predictor", "Subsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.780548039791498*^9, 
  3.78054805653337*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"e4ef5e0f-2227-4c39-ad24-\
1866e1835f58"],

Cell["\<\
In order to test the performance of the trained predictor, we use part of the \
data to define a test data. The example data explicitly contains a test \
dataset corresponding to a selection of 168 examples.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7805483886824093`*^9, 
  3.7805484962524033`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"87284e05-d541-4b92-9318-\
db18c69bc33e"],

